# Auto-Reload Browser After Code Changes

After making any code changes to the Tamagotchi project, always reload the browser so the user can see updates immediately.

1. Make the code edit(s)
2. Call `browser_reload` via the `cursor-ide-browser` MCP with `{"take_screenshot_afterwards": true}`
3. Wait ~3 seconds, then take a screenshot to confirm the page loaded correctly

Never skip the reload step — the user should see their changes without having to ask.
